<plot>For Charlie, Darby and Steve, their entire friendship consists of nothing more than daily water cooler discussions of hockey. When the infamous NHL lockout effectively ends the 2004/2005 season - and life as they know it - these men realize that they have nothing better to do than get to know each other, with interesting results. This short comedy explores their hilarious adventures and intriguing discoveries during the year without hockey.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?602716</url></doc>
